'''德頓街'''（{{lang-en|Tufton Street}}）位於[[英國|英國]][[伦敦|伦敦]][[西敏|西敏]]，因聚集{{tsl|en|Euroscepticism in the United Kingdom|英國疑歐主義}}和[[右派|右派]][[智庫|智庫]]，而被視為[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]支持者的中心。大多組織都設在德頓街55號，亦有在57號。

== 德頓街55號 ==
德頓街55號是一幢[[乔治王时代|乔治王时代]]排屋，目前由商人理查·史密擁有<ref name=":0">{{cite news|last1=Bawden|first1=Tom|title=The address where Eurosceptics and climate change sceptics rub shoulders|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/eu-referendum-eurosceptics-climate-change-sceptics-55-tufton-street-westminster-a6866021.html|accessdate=2020-09-02|work=The Independent|date=2016-02-10|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313153628/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/eu-referendum-eurosceptics-climate-change-sceptics-55-tufton-street-westminster-a6866021.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年代起，多個脫歐和[[氣候變化|氣候變化]]的智庫進駐排屋，當中九個智庫合稱「九實體」（{{tsl|en|TaxPayers' Alliance|納稅聯盟}}、新文化論壇、{{tsl|en|Civitas (think tank)|公民體}}、{{tsl|en|Adam Smith Institute|亞當·史密研究所}}、{{tsl|en|Leave Means Leave|脫就是脫}}、{{tsl|en|Global Warming Policy Foundation|全球暖化政策基金會}}、脫歐中心、{{tsl|en|Centre for Policy Studies|政策研究中心}}和{{tsl|en|Institute for Economic Affairs|財務研究所}}），每兩週舉行會議協調政策和宣傳<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Revealed: how the UK’s powerful right-wing think tanks and Conservative MPs work together|url=https://www.opendemocracy.net/uk/brexitinc/peter-geoghegan-adam-ramsay/revealed-how-uk-s-powerful-right-wing-think-tanks-and-conse|date=2018-07-31|language=en|website=openDemocracy|access-date=2018-10-07|archive-date=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207090629/https://www.opendemocracy.net/uk/brexitinc/peter-geoghegan-adam-ramsay/revealed-how-uk-s-powerful-right-wing-think-tanks-and-conse|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=55 Tufton Street|url=https://www.desmog.co.uk/55-tufton-street|language=en|website=DeSmog UK|access-date=2019-06-27|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116060055/https://www.desmog.co.uk/55-tufton-street|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

